      <odd id="aspace_30214f84146f94e70d136daaed323ce7">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 10-B (YRG 10-B), Records of Sheffield Scientific School classes.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_fd92b5c9656accb898d61bff310dc844">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were donated by Howard Gambrill, 2004; family of Watson F. Kinney, 2008.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
